NOTE ON PROBLEM CONTENT

This project indexes the Striver A2Z / TUF+ DSA sheet by problem name, topic and
sheet section, and links to takeuforward.org. The sheet itself, its ordering and
its editorial content belong to takeuforward (Striver) and are not covered by
this license. This is an unofficial, independent companion tracker with no
affiliation to or endorsement from takeuforward.

Problem links to LeetCode, Codeforces and other judges are provided for
convenience; those platforms' content belongs to them.
